  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Worldless unfolds in a newborn universe where entities are locked in an eternal conflict fueled by the polarizing nature of their attractions. These encounters can trigger an unstable exchange of polarities with transformations that are unpredictable and full of mysterious consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this stylized 2D  platformer, you will explore intricate and interconnected realms brimming with secrets and mysteries. Master a rich set of abilities such as dashing and wall jumping to traverse these abstract landscapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along your journey, you will face beings determined to stop you as you search for your place within this universe. Battles blend classic turn based strategy with real time action elements, demanding deep knowledge of  mechanics for a thrilling and strategic combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/cbe5dee8318de973eb5692186c88cfb9.webp?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=25 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover unimaginable possibilities by dashing, jumping, and weaving through surreal environments on a quest for transcendence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/218494041517f7e3dbe29ec10a3411d4.poster.avif?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/218494041517f7e3dbe29ec10a3411d4.webm?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/218494041517f7e3dbe29ec10a3411d4.mp4?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/74aa1eea057ca5f13f19a8d591541e83.webp?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=25 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your growth through a deep and rewarding talent tree designed to fit your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/9fe7ed55045b8cd93da9c833d94f2506.poster.avif?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/9fe7ed55045b8cd93da9c833d94f2506.webm?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/9fe7ed55045b8cd93da9c833d94f2506.mp4?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/a38967c39f54bafe577e01d4482cf513.webp?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=25 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in fast-paced  battles where mastering your attacks and defenses is key to overcoming your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/e0c565923764287e00a76ba33371408e.poster.avif?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/e0c565923764287e00a76ba33371408e.webm?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/e0c565923764287e00a76ba33371408e.mp4?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/77444384b461ff520a72643ed64cfdd8.webp?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=25 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lose yourself in haunting yet beautiful melodies that connect you deeply to every corner of the world of Worldless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/d4e7237520c9b58fdd21b8a56b435ee8.poster.avif?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/d4e7237520c9b58fdd21b8a56b435ee8.webm?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/d4e7237520c9b58fdd21b8a56b435ee8.mp4?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Worldless unfolds in a newborn universe where entities are locked in an eternal conflict fueled by the polarizing nature of their attractions. These encounters can trigger an unstable exchange of polarities with transformations that are unpredictable and full of mysterious consequences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this stylized 2D  platformer, you will explore intricate and interconnected realms brimming with secrets and mysteries. Master a rich set of abilities such as dashing and wall jumping to traverse these abstract landscapes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along your journey, you will face beings determined to stop you as you search for your place within this universe. Battles blend classic turn based strategy with real time action elements, demanding deep knowledge of  mechanics for a thrilling and strategic combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/cbe5dee8318de973eb5692186c88cfb9.webp?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=25 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover unimaginable possibilities by dashing, jumping, and weaving through surreal environments on a quest for transcendence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/218494041517f7e3dbe29ec10a3411d4.poster.avif?t=1758539643\" width=780 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/218494041517f7e3dbe29ec10a3411d4.webm?t=1758539643\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1898500/extras/218494041517f7e3dbe